{"tid":815563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白宮聯署]滬獨黨員關押精神病院 酷刑電擊","createTime":"2018-09-12T06:58:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T08:38:22.000Z","uid":47359,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb6b96da4a6e12b1e9b7345b19eacf7a535e7ab","tid":815563,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:58:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2184287351850635&amp;id=2048175568795148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2184287351850635%26id%3D2048175568795148&d=9N5G4lBSDNQ9%2FhAsjx6PYxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=47f3df99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2184287351850635&amp;id=2048175568795148</a><br />\n<br />\n【聯結獨立力量，對抗中共殖民】<br />\n<br />\n日前上海民族黨發出緊急聲明就旗下的一名民主黨成員胡誠宜於今年7月回上海後遭到迫害。目前更證實「他已『被精神病』，關押在上海市精神衛生中心。據悉他還遭受電擊酷刑。」發出強烈譴責。<br />\n<br />\n並於白宮官網為他建立了一個「釋放胡誠宜」的簽名請願，迫使美國作出行動，向中共施壓。<br />\n<br />\n現時胡誠宜生命危在旦夕，望一眾獨派同道能施以援手，聯署聲援胡誠宜。"},{"pid":"60eab87bd9e15794b58f5bbfe2fd878dd2e6c0f1","tid":815563,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:58:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2094a3829d888bd76dd73a6a380e9aa338f38ba5","tid":815563,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:59:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c170edf75f364848c573f398b775ff88af9b69","tid":815563,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T06:59:28.000Z","msg":"其實只要上證指數低過100就完成"},{"pid":"4045a623705fd4a280b63e1d49dbb7d3d09257b6","tid":815563,"uid":26770,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T07:09:58.000Z","msg":"簽左<br />\n我極